            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It has been a very enriching and fruitful experience while working in Golden Heights School. Overall environment of the school is oriented toward the growth and development of children under the leadership of our esteemed Principal and Senior Management. The work culture is very conducive for growth as the staff members are quite supportive and collaborative in our day today functioning. It’s an institution which strives towards excellence and development of children.\nIt’s a school where you love to work, as it gives you the freedom to explore your creativity in the field of education and provides ample opportunity for self development. Also from time to time it organizes workshops on latest trends of education which provides us the  opportunity to  grow personally and professionally.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
