            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Being a teacher at golden heights has been incredible. Everything about golden height is excellent.The school organises various fun and knowledgeable events for students and teachers which help them to interact with each other. The school staff is helpful and polite. It has been 10-15 years I have worked at golden heights and it has always been amazing.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
