            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Golden Heights School is one of the most renowned institutions of  Gurugram.The school focuses on the overall development of a child. Teachers are well trained and meet all the needs of the students by adopting various teaching methodologies and technology. It is a new age learning school. The school is having a positive environment with all the facilities. Love n light",
          "publisher": {
