            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had the pleasure of visiting Golden Heights school on number of occasions. I have participated in their yearly carnivals which is something I always look forward too. It is  an opportunity to interact with the teachers and other staff members who are really very humble and dedicated. I also had a pleasure of visiting the school for an external viva and got an opportunity to interact with students. It was clear that they are well schooled.\n\nGood communication, team work, and effective schools take a lot of hard work. So congratulations to the whole team of Golden Heights school !",
